high_descs: Turn around to reach the sink on the right.
Pick up the mug from the sink.
Turn left and head right to reach the bathroom sink on the left.
Wash the mug in the sink and take it out.
Turn left to reach the dresser on the left under the TV,
Put the mug on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Put the washed mug on the dresser.

high_descs: Turn right and go straight and make a right turn near sink.
Pick up mug from the sink.
Go left and head straight towards the wall. After that, turn left and walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right.
Wash mug on the sink and take it back
Turn right and head straight, make left and then again hang left towards the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Washing mug and placing it clean

high_descs: Turn around, walk straight until there's sink on your right, and face it
Pick up a mug from the sink.
Turn left, walk around the corner on the right, enter the bathroom on the right and approach the sink
Put the mug in the sink.
Leave the bathroom, take a few steps straight and then go left to the leftmost dresser under a TV.
Place the mug on the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Get a mug to the dresser.
